### Create a restaurant
POST http://localhost:4000/restaurants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Oceanview Bistro",
  "address": "123 Harbor Lane",
  "phone": "555-1234",
  "cuisine": "Seafood"
}

### Get all restaurants
GET http://localhost:4000/restaurants

### Create a table
POST http://localhost:4000/tables
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number": 5,
  "seats": 4,
  "location": "Patio"
}

### Create a menu item for restaurant 1
POST http://localhost:4000/restaurants/1/menus
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Grilled Salmon",
  "description": "Served with seasonal vegetables",
  "price": 22.5,
  "category": "Entree"
}

### Create an order
POST http://localhost:4000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "restaurantId": 1,
  "tableId": 1,
  "items": [
    { "menuId": 1, "quantity": 2 }
  ],
  "customerName": "Alex",
  "status": "pending"
}

### Retrieve all orders
GET http://localhost:4000/orders
